1. *Gledao* sam uživo koncert. (I watched a live concert.)
2. Na televiziji se emituje uživo. (It is being broadcasted live on TV.)
3. Zalazak sunca je posebno lep kada se gleda uživo. (The sunset is especially beautiful when watched live.)
4. Svi smo pratili *uživo* prenos utakmice. (We all followed the live broadcast of the game.)
5. Slušam *uživo* radio. (I'm listening to a live radio.)
6. Televizijski prenos je bio *uživo*. (The TV broadcast was live.)